=3D"ssrcss-1myx8lm-Row enh46940"><div><div><div data-component=3D"text-bloc=
k" class=3D"text-block ssrcss-17u89h5-TextWrapper e1ekt5r40"><p>Whether you=
=E2=80=99re planning chicken, beef, pork or lamb for your Sunday roast, fin=
d out the ideal meat cooking times and temperatures with our easy-to-use ca=
lculator. No maths required!</p><p>Simply select your meat and cut from the=
 menu and type in the weight in kg (if it's a bird tell us the stuffed weig=
ht). If you're cooking beef or lamb, tell us if you want it well done, medi=
um or rare. Then click "calculate" to find out the browning and cooking tim=
es and temperatures and the resting time. Tap "checking for doneness" to fi=
nd out what the internal temperature of the meat should be when it's ready.=
</p></div></div></div></div><div data-layout=3D"single" class=3D"ssrcss-1my=
